---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Writing"
  description="Muhammad Seedat's writing — The Sand & Silicon Byte newsletter, Substack, and LinkedIn."
>

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="header-eyebrow mono">Writing</div>
    <h1 class="page-title">Where the thinking lives</h1>
    <p class="page-desc">
      The newsletter is the owned asset. Everything else feeds it.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Newsletter -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="wrap">

    <div class="section-label">The Sand &amp; Silicon Byte · Primary</div>

    <div class="platform-feature">
      <div class="platform-meta mono">
        <span class="platform-badge">Weekly newsletter</span>
        <span class="platform-status">·</span>
        <span>Beehiiv · Free</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="platform-name">The Sand &amp; Silicon Byte</h2>
      <p class="platform-desc">
        A weekly letter at the intersection of AI, the Gulf, and education. One big idea. Three signals.
        An ancient thread. A prompt you can use this week. Written from inside the systems — not from a think tank.
      </p>
      <p class="platform-desc">
        This is the owned asset. No algorithm. Direct to your inbox. Everything else — LinkedIn, Baseera,
        Substack — feeds this. The newsletter is where readers become a community.
      </p>
      <a href="https://thesandandsiliconbyte.beehiiv.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-dark" style="margin-top: 8px; display: inline-block;">
        Subscribe free →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- Other Platforms -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="wrap">

    <div class="section-label">Other platforms</div>

    <ul class="platforms-list">

      <li class="platform-item">
        <div class="platform-body">
          <div class="platform-item-meta mono">LinkedIn · @southafricanbedouin</div>
          <div class="platform-item-title">Daily &amp; bi-weekly content</div>
          <div class="platform-item-desc">The primary public voice. Where Baseera editions are published first, alongside daily signal posts across all four content pillars.</div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/southafricanbedouin" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="platform-arrow">→</a>
      </li>

      <li class="platform-item">
        <div class="platform-body">
          <div class="platform-item-meta mono">Substack · southafricanbedouin</div>
          <div class="platform-item-title">Raw thinking</div>
          <div class="platform-item-desc">Where the ideas start. Irregular, impulse-driven, less polished. Raw thinking before it becomes content. The discovery layer.</div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://southafricanbedouin.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="platform-arrow">→</a>
      </li>

      <li class="platform-item">
        <div class="platform-body">
          <div class="platform-item-meta mono">Baseera · بصيرة</div>
          <div class="platform-item-title">Distilled reading</div>
          <div class="platform-item-desc">One article. Three layers: The Finding, The Pattern, The Signal. Published bi-weekly. One idea, fully thought through.</div>
        </div>
        <a href="/baseera" class="platform-arrow">→</a>
      </li>

    </ul>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- On the writing -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="wrap">

    <div class="section-label">On the writing itself</div>

    <div class="writing-note">
      <p>
        Everything I write follows the same principle: <strong>I am the witness, not the hero.</strong>
        The content is about the pattern, the system, the idea I noticed — not about my years of
        experience or my journey. The reader is the protagonist.
      </p>
      <p>
        The voice is direct. No performed reflection. No announcement phrases.
        The thought delivered, not announced.
      </p>
      <p>
        Long-form always opens with <em>As-salamu alaykum</em>. That is not a stylistic choice.
        It is who I am.
      </p>
      <blockquote class="writing-quote">
        "The systems you build today determine who leads tomorrow."
      </blockquote>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 64px 0 48px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .header-eyebrow {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sand);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .page-desc {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Feature Platform */
  .platform-feature {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--sand);
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  .platform-meta {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sand);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .platform-status { color: var(--rule); }

  .platform-name {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .platform-desc {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  /* Platforms List */
  .platforms-list { list-style: none; }

  .platform-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: start;
    padding: 28px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.12s;
  }

  .platform-item:first-child { padding-top: 0; }
  .platform-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .platform-item:hover .platform-item-title { color: var(--sand-dark); }

  .platform-item-meta {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sand);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .platform-item-title {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .platform-item-desc {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .platform-arrow {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--rule);
    margin-top: 8px;
    transition: color 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
    display: block;
  }
  .platform-item:hover .platform-arrow { color: var(--sand); transform: translateX(4px); }

  /* Writing Note */
  .writing-note {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .writing-note p { margin-bottom: 1.2em; }
  .writing-note strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }
  .writing-note em { font-style: italic; }

  .writing-quote {
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--sand);
    background: var(--sand-pale);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    line-height: 1.6;
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .platform-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .platform-arrow { display: none; }
  }
</style>
